/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605801ecb1a0e93df715da07ac275fb1ec93e6a2","tid":414863,"uid":26586,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:19:47.000Z","msg":"三寶讀d野其實唔係話難同深<br />\n講難同深，我相信pure  science難度高更多<br />\n點解入面d人讀到咁chur係因為身邊d同學個個都高分入來，收生高自然拉高左個學習氣氛同標準。<br />\n但係讀緊既人就知，d prof.同讀既野，質素真係得啖笑。"},{"pid":"b49db50fd88f376195db693b5cc896a9d5f4315b","tid":414863,"uid":87069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾年AL<br />\n醫科都係收  幾個C 咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反 IT係神科<br />\n收straight 三條A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSource? 中大醫科9x年就收BBC既，幾個C好似無咁過份<br />\n<br />\n亦係嗰期Civil/ IT收 3條A..."},{"pid":"76701aea5b33b78cf5d497f3c72c8fecc61834c3","tid":414863,"uid":104885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:35:21.000Z","msg":"三十年河東三十年河西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能十幾年後又會個個爭住讀it"},{"pid":"5402262b1de02b9782d364b999d979e65c20733f","tid":414863,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三寶讀d野其實唔係話難同深<br />\n講難同深，我相信pure  science難度高更多<br />\n點解入面d人讀到咁chur係因為身邊d同學個個都高分入來，收生高自然拉高左個學習氣氛同標準。<br />\n但係讀緊既人就知，d prof.同讀既野，質素真係得啖笑。</blockquote><br />\n東大都有人讀到 知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee34cb216b3d7186b4241ac3128e53d9c57fd43d","tid":414863,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"最筍都係末代AL個屆<br />\n全部神科加位而且冇IB撚爭位<br />\n相傳3條B入到dental"},{"pid":"70741a60825261fdd05906ab88bab99e2c9b3448","tid":414863,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾年AL<br />\n醫科都係收  幾個C 咋<img src=\"/asset