佢ug時已經講讀嗰科啲野讀到接近醫嘅level<br />\n但實際做視光師唔洗應用到咁深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n視光不嬲都chur <br />\n<br />\n而家啲人覺得chur 我覺得係成個allied health 專業化咗 唔同人都想分擔醫生嘅工作所以讀多咗好多出到去唔會用到嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸讀緊"},{"pid":"ca0e9b07fd990b0c7d40647ff83dbef2d0d8f0bf","tid":414863,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇成個檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無呀<br />\n<br />\n我只係知<br />\n<br />\nhku law收～CCC<br />\ncity law收 ～dee<br />\ncu medic收～bbc<br />\n<br />\n反而最高係cu engine／ust gbus qfin 呢堆，收aaa－aaB</blockquote><br />\n其實讀law出路都唔係話好好<br />\nbarrister 完全係靠父幹<br />\nsolicitor 香港太多人, 例如外國啲野雞U都要同香港爭飯食<br />\n我識人佢做soli做到三十幾歲都係搵四皮幾<br />\n最後唯有轉做compliance</blockquote><br />\nGBus都係 大把阿爸老細/高層<br />\n仲有MBA 公司中高層玩意<br />\n應該唔洗講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804757e25ca6bf9d3022f9fd2a34cd4a13c3098f","tid":414863,"uid":43652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三寶讀d野其實唔係話難同深<br />\n講難同深，我相信pure  science難度高更多<br />\n點解入面d人讀到咁chur係因為身邊d同學個個都高分入來，收生高自然拉高左個學習氣氛同標準。<br />\n但係讀緊既人就知，d prof.同讀既野，質素真係得啖笑。</blockquote><br />\n識人視光讀到PhD<br />\n佢ug時已經講讀嗰科啲野讀到接近醫嘅level<br />\n但實際做視光師唔洗應用到咁深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n視光不嬲都chur <br />\n<br />\n而家啲人覺得chur 我覺得係成個allied health 專業化咗 唔同人都想分擔醫生嘅工作所以讀多咗好多出到去唔會用到嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸讀緊</blockquote><br />\n五寶都要讀anat Physi patho<br />\n有幾多會真係用得著?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab6f8f